      • VARS

        static final String VARS
        The IVariable[] identifying the variables for which the referenced values in binding sets are joined with the dictionary (whenever they are bound to mocked IDs). be materialized. When null or not specified, ALL variables will be materialized. This may not be an empty array as that would imply that there is no need to use this operator.
